high_descs: walk to the center of the table ahead
grab a knife off of the table
look down a bit at the table
slice the apple up into slices on the left side of the table
turn right and walk over to the sink
place the knife inside of the sink
turn back around and walk over to the kitchen table again
grab an apple slice off of the kitchen table
turn right and walk over to the sink, but then turn left to face the microwave
place the apple slice inside of the microwave, microwave it, then take it back out
move to forwards and turn right so that the meeting between the sink and the kitchen counter is in your center view
place the apple slice inside of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved apple slice inside of the sink

high_descs: Walk across the room to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn to face the apple on the table.
Cut the apple into 3 slices.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room and face the table on the right.
Pick up a slice of the apple on the table.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the apple slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the piece of apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple as well as put it in the sink.

high_descs: Head straight to the table
Grab the knife off of the table
Look down at the table
Cut the apple into slices
Turn right and head to the sink
Put the knife into the sink
Turn around and head to the table
Grab one of the apple slices
Turn right and head to the microwave
Heat the apple in the microwave and then take it out
Turn right and head to the sink
Put the apple into the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a sliced apple into the sink

high_descs: Walk to the table in front of you
Grab the large knife that's near the toaster
Look down at the table
Cut the apple on the table into three slices
Turn right and stop at the sink
Put the knife into the sink
Turn around and stop at the table
Grab one of the apple slices
Turn right and head to the microwave
Put the apple in the microwave and heat it. Open the microwave and take the apple out.
Head to the sink on the right
Place the apple in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting an apple in the sink

high_descs: Go to the table in front of you.
Pick up the knife nearest to the toaster.
Move back slightly from the table.
Cut the apple into thirds.
Turn to your right and take the knife to the sink.
Put the knife into the sink.
Return to the table that is holding the toaster and apple.
Pick up the center third of the apple.
Take the piece of apple to the microwave on the counter left of the sink.
Cook the piece of apple in the microwave.
Move to your right to the sink.
Put the piece of apple into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a piece of cooked apple into the sink.
